property.value: Evolution - Put on one of your Nature creatures. Double Breaker Unleash - Each of your other creatures gets +3000 power until the end of the turn and can't be blocked this turn by creatures that have less power than it.

property.value: (This card enters your mana zone tapped.) Double Breaker Defense Drop - When this creature enters the battle zone, search your deck. You may put a non-evolution creature that is level 3 or less and has "Blocker" from your deck into the battle zone. Then shuffle your deck.

property.value: (This card enters your mana zone tapped.) Double Breaker Aura of Dread - When this creature enters the battle zone, all your creatures get "Slayer" until the end of the turn. Ethereal - This creature can't be blocked.
